# Governance Rules

1. Load `SECURITY.md` before any implementation work
2. One persona per task — mismatch → STOP
3. UC DDL only by Unity Catalog persona
4. SQL reads via `config/queries/` — never custom warehouse endpoints for SELECT
5. No secrets in repo, logs, or prompts
